==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Numbness
<hw>Numb"ness</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>The condition of
being numb; that state of a living body in which it loses, wholly or in
part, the power of feeling or motion.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>numdah</ent>⟦br⟧
